Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • Database

  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    The Database class creates a connection to a database and contains methods that allow a user to save earthquake and observatory data to a database and retrieve the data. It contains a method that recreates a Monitoring object from the database by retrieving earthquake and observatory information from the database and recreating earthquake and observatory objects to store in the Monitoring object
    Author:
    Setriakor Addom and Ohemaa Akoto
